Graphics object."
}], "Usage",ExpressionUUID->"ab9c169c-ab10-4f3f-a993-1bd7a8cf4eb5"],

Cell["\<\
input may be a KnotData specification (e.g. Knot[3,1]), a PD/DTCode/GaussCode \
from the KnotTheory package, a 3D space curve (or list of curves, for a \
link), a native Knoodle PD code, or a PlanarDiagramComplex from \
KnoodleSimplify.\
\>", "Notes",ExpressionUUID->"cd83dfd2-33bb-4244-bbb9-099263d411b7"]
}, Open  ]],

